address2: 5th Floor No. 8, Fuyou Road Huangpu District
longBusinessSummary: Yida China Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, develops and operates residential properties and business parks in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Property Development; Property Investment; Business Park Operation and Management; and Construction, and Decoration and Landscaping segments. The Property Development segment develops and sells properties. The Property Investment segment invests in and rents properties. The Business Park Operation and Management segment provides operation and management services to the business park projects owned by the local governments or other independent third parties. The Construction, and Decoration and Landscaping segment engages in property construction business, and the provision of interior decoration services to property buyers, as well as landscaping services to property projects. Its property portfolio includes multifunctional integrated residential community projects, office properties, and residential properties. Yida China Holdings Limited was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
